OL,5, French fashion brand Louis Vuitton has 
OL,6, hired Grammy-winning producer, rapper, 
OL,7, singer and songwriter Pharrell Williams
OL,8, as its menswear creative director.     
OL,10,FThe label described Williams as "a     
OL,11,Fvisionary whose creative universes     
OL,12,Fexpand from music to art, and to       
OL,13,Ffashion".                              
OL,15,FHe is also the co-founder of the       
OL,16,Fstreetwear brand Billionaire Boys Club.
OL,18,FThe Louis Vuitton role was previously  
OL,19,Fheld by high-profile designer Virgil   
OL,20,FAbloh, who died in 2021.               
